<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وإِفْشَاءُ سِرٍ ثُمَّ لَعْنُ مُقَيَّدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَفُحْشٌ وَمَكْر وَالْبِذَا وَخَدِيعَةٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وسُخْرِيًّةٌ والهُزْؤُ وَالْكِذْبَ قَيِّدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِغَيْرِ خِدَاعِ الْكَافِرِينَ بِحَرْبِهِم<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَللعرْس أَوْ إِصْلاحِ أَهْلِ التَّنَكُّدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ مِزْمَارٌ وَشُبَّابَةٌ وَمَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يُضَاهِيهِمَا مِنْ آلَةِ اللَّهْوِ والرَّدي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَلَوْ لَمْ يُقَارِنْهَا غِنَاءٌ جَمِيعُهَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَمنْهَا ذَوُو الأَوْتَارِ دُونَ تَقَيُّدِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَلا بَأْسَ بالشِّعْرِ الْمُبَاحَِ وَحِفْظِهِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَصَنْعَتِهِ مَنْ رَدَّ ذَلِكَ يَعْتَدِي<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَقَدْ سَمَعَ الْمُخْتَارُ شِعْر َصَحَابَةٍ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَتَشْبِيبِهُمِ مِن غَيْرِ تَعِيِينِ خُرَّدِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَحَظْرَ الْهِجَا والْمَدْحِ بالزُّورِ وَالْخَنَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَتَشْبِيبِهِ بِالأَجْنَبِيَّاتِ أَكِّدِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَوَصْفِ الزِّنَا وَالْخَمْرِ وَالْمُرْدِ وَالنِّسَا الْـ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>ـفَتِيَّاتِ أَوْ نَوْحِ التَّسَخُّطِ مُورَدِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَأَوْجِبْ عَن الْمَحْضُورِ كَفَّ جَوَارِحٍ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَنَدْبٌ عَنِ الْمَكْرُوهِ غَيْرَ مُشَدِّدِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَأَمْرُكَ بِالْمَعْرُوفِ وَالنَّهْيِ يَا فَتَى<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>عَنِ الْمُنْكَرِ اجْعَلْ فَرْضَ عَيْنٍ تُسَدَّدِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>